    "description": "WeWork India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Property Advisor for our Bhopal operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout WeWork India:\nWeWork India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with WeWork India!",
